  "policyContent": "<div class=\"policy-box\"><div class=\"pb-title\"><span class=\"pb-icon\">📣</span>微信小游戏</div><div class=\"pb-body\"><b>本周政策：</b><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/9Mc9Kzb2Zukri_24TvdRCg\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"policy-link\">5月27日开发者大会</a>核心数据：MAU突破5亿，开发者超50万。平台战略转向\"从连接到长青\"。<br><b>IAP新游激励：</b>首发新游最高5000万流水不分成+2000万激励金。<a href=\"https://developers.weixin.qq.com/minigame/introduction/commercialization/\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"policy-link\">查看激励政策 →</a><br><b>IAA激励：</b>最高90%分成。新增回流政策。<br><b>PC战略：</b>独占用户40%，ARPU超移动130%。</div></div><div class=\"policy-box\"><div class=\"pb-title\"><span class=\"pb-icon\">🍎</span>苹果</div><div class=\"pb-body\"><a href=\"https://developer.apple.com/cn/app-store/small-business-program/\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"policy-link\">标准佣金25%</a>，<a href=\"https://developer.apple.com/cn/app-store/small-business-program/\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"policy-link\">小型厂商15%</a>。iOS支付流程已跑通，苹果抽15%。</div></div><div class=\"policy-box\"><div class=\"pb-title\"><span class=\"pb-icon\">🎵</span>抖音</div><div class=\"pb-body\">历史任务金5月激活。<a href=\"https://partner.open-douyin.com/docs/resource/zh-CN/mini-game/guide/minigame/examineguide\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"policy-link\">Q1 IAP最高40%消耗赠款</a>。任务金限时激励至6月30日。</div></div><div class=\"policy-box\"><div class=\"pb-title\"><span class=\"pb-icon\">📜</span>版号</div><div class=\"pb-body\">158款获批（国产154+进口4）。累计779个，同比增19.66%。模拟经营约17款过审。</div></div>",
